      <section eId="sec_CC-3286">
        <num>CC 3286</num>
        <heading>3286. Â Property susceptible of mortgage</heading>
        <subsection eId="CC-3286__subsec_1">
          <num>(1)</num>
          <content>
            <p>A corporeal immovable with its component parts.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CC-3286__subsec_2">
          <num>(2)</num>
          <content>
            <p>A usufruct of a corporeal immovable.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CC-3286__subsec_3">
          <num>(3)</num>
          <content>
            <p>A servitude of right of use with the rights that the holder of the servitude may have in the buildings and other constructions on the land.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CC-3286__subsec_4">
          <num>(4)</num>
          <content>
            <p>The lessee's rights in a lease of an immovable with his rights in the buildings and other constructions on the immovable.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CC-3286__subsec_5">
          <num>(5)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Property made susceptible of conventional mortgage by special law.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
